Text: Re Hello againYes I liked him a lot I wish he were more conveniently located and that he was on my insurance network Ive got to go out of network if I keep seeing him I have a pediatrician close by and I like her but shes new out of her residency and doesnt know as much as Injac does He had a lot more information to give me on several items I had talked to her about Where are you going Vacation I hope Connor has mommyitis He doesnt want me to ever leave him and its too restrictive Our day a week nanny went on vacation for weeks and now hes upset if she has him How quickly they change I guess thats the good news also My phone is they wouldnt give me a number to my surprise Oh well there are worse things than having a difficult phone number See you soon maybe Kathy Original Message From To Sent Thursday October AM Subject RE Hello again Hi Kathy Thanks for the message it was great to see you yesterday Sam is fine the doctor thinks some steroids would help Yuk Did you like Dr Injac My kids love him Im leaving in about an hour and will not be back until the middle of next week but will write then and we can set up a time for lunch Talk to you soon Elizabeth Sager Original Message From Kathy Ellis Cook ENRON Sent Wednesday October PM To Sager Elizabeth Subject Hello again Hi Liz It was fun catching up with you at DrInjaks Like you I married a geologist my dad and brotherinlaw are also geologists Its a nice change from lawyers I hope Sam is doing OK What did the doctor say to do for him Let me know what your schedule is like and we can meet some time Im fairly flexible but have a nanny only days per week so the rest of the time Connor is with me My little shadow Ciao Kathy Ellis Cook This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant IS IT POSSIBLEI dont know if this is true but on the chance that it is wanted to send this to you In a message dated PM Mountain Daylight Time writes cc Subject FW Malls on Its so sad that I feel like I need to send out a precautionary email like this without any real proof that this is even a concern But better safe than sorry Hi All I think you all know that I dont send out hoaxes and dont do the reactionary thing and send out anything that crosses my path This one however is a friend of a friend and Ive given it enough credibility in my mind that Im writing it up and sending it out to all of you My friends friend was dating a guy from Afghanistan up until a month ago She had a date with him around and was stood up She was understandably upset and went to his home to find it completely emptied On she received a letter from her boyfriend explaining that he wished he could tell her why he had left and that he was sorry it had to be like that The part worth mentioning is that he BEGGED her not to geton any commercial airlines on and to not to go any malls on Halloween As soon as everything happened on the th she called the FBI and has since turned over the letter This is not an email that Ive received and decided to pass on This came from a phone conversation with a longtime friend of mine last night I may be wrong and I hope I am However with one of his warnings being correct and devastating Im not willing to take the chance on the second and wanted to make sure that people I cared about had the same information that I did Laura Katsis Implementation Specialist
